  <brief_title>Staff Opinions and Knowledge Concerning Organ and Tissue Harvesting: an Investigation Among the Patient Care Personnel in the South-Mediterranean Region of France</brief_title>
  <official_title>Staff Opinions and Knowledge Concerning Organ and Tissue Harvesting: an Investigation Among the Patient Care Personnel in the South-Mediterranean Region of France</official_title>
